If you are using the [Maven Shade Plugin][1], you can a [filter][2], which will allow you to filter which artifacts get shaded, but as well as which classes to exclude or include.

Here&#39;s the example they provide:

&lt;!-- language: lang-xml --&gt;

    &lt;filters&gt;
      &lt;filter&gt;
        &lt;artifact&gt;junit:junit&lt;/artifact&gt;
        &lt;includes&gt;
          &lt;include&gt;org/junit/**&lt;/include&gt;
        &lt;/includes&gt;
        &lt;excludes&gt;
          &lt;exclude&gt;org/junit/experimental/**&lt;/exclude&gt;
        &lt;/excludes&gt;
      &lt;/filter&gt;
    &lt;/filters&gt;


  [1]: https://maven.apache.org/plugins/maven-shade-plugin/
  [2]: https://maven.apache.org/plugins/maven-shade-plugin/shade-mojo.html#filters

You should be able to use the [maven-dependency-plugin](http://maven.apache.org/plugins/maven-dependency-plugin/usage.html#The_dependency%3aunpack_mojo) like this:

&lt;!-- language: lang-xml --&gt;

    &lt;build&gt;
        &lt;plugins&gt;
            &lt;plugin&gt;
                &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;
                &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-dependency-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;
                &lt;version&gt;2.10&lt;/version&gt;
                &lt;executions&gt;
                    &lt;execution&gt;
                        &lt;id&gt;unpack&lt;/id&gt;
                        &lt;phase&gt;package&lt;/phase&gt;
                        &lt;goals&gt;
                            &lt;goal&gt;unpack&lt;/goal&gt;
                        &lt;/goals&gt;
                        &lt;configuration&gt;
                            &lt;artifactItems&gt;
                                &lt;artifactItem&gt;
                                    &lt;groupId&gt;&lt;!--dependency groupId--&gt;&lt;/groupId&gt;
                                    &lt;artifactId&gt;&lt;!--dependency artifactId--&gt;&lt;/artifactId&gt;
                                    &lt;version&gt;&lt;!--depedency version--&gt;&lt;/version&gt;
                                    &lt;includes&gt;**/*Client*.java&lt;/includes&gt;
                                &lt;/artifactItem&gt;
                            &lt;/artifactItems&gt;
                        &lt;/configuration&gt;
                    &lt;/execution&gt;
                &lt;/executions&gt;
            &lt;/plugin&gt;
